title: Belzepub
typeOfFood: American, Western, Fast food, Beer/Wine, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. A rock and punk themed bar serving tapas, burgers, salads. Vegan choices are a burger, chili, hummus, fries with soyanaise, and a breakfast; ask if uses the same fryer for meatstuff if order fries and onion rings. A house-made soy mixture is used in vegetarian/vegan dishes. Loud at night. Smoking cigarettes allowed.
